        {
            "type": "note",
            "text": "; This is a demonstration of how tts_seq_viewer can work for a simple earth orbiting mission."
        },
        {
            "type": "note",
            "text": "; The details of this sequence don't matter much, but for context, it is meant to represent"
        },
        {
            "type": "note",
            "text": "; a simple spacecraft setting up comm for an X-Band contact with Wallops ground station."
        },
        {
            "type": "note",
            "text": ";"
        },
        {
            "type": "note",
            "text": "; This is a realtively timed sequence because it could be used at any given time depending on"
        },
        {
            "type": "note",
            "text": "; the exact geometries and view periods to Wallops."
        },
        {
            "type": "note",
            "text": ";"
        },
        {
            "type": "note",
            "text": "; In a real sequence, one might expect metatdata to also go here."
        },
        {
            "type": "note",
            "text": ";------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------"
        },
